node.text: After 5 years and 555 episodes, As Per Usual on @webtoonofficial has ended! Most of the comics I’ve posted on Instagram have been comics I made for Webtoon. There’s lots more I haven’t posted here, so go check them out if you want! I’ll still keep drawing comics and working on whatever’s next, even though I usually feel like the 4th panel. 😭 but all that aside, I’m seriously so grateful for Webtoon supporting my art for the past five years, and all the sweet readers whose comments made it all worth it.💖

node.text: Happy #AAPIHeritageMonth! Learning your native language to communicate with your family and celebrate your culture is great, but doing it to fulfill your frivolous internet shopping needs is also valid lol 💖 there's more stories like this in my book, Be Everything At Once, about my time as a wee ESL child in Texas, my reverse culture shock returning to Korea as an adult, and quitting my job to move back to america to draw comics (a bold, dumb idea you can only do in your 20s)!

node.text: Honored to collaborate with @perryfellow to celebrate 20 years of PBF comics!! As a tween, I remember going on pbfcomics.com to read new comics before Instagram was even a twinkle in zuck’s eyes. PBF was a huge influence on me as I’m sure it was for so many other webcomics! Thanks Nick!! 🐢#PBF20years

node.text:
GIVEAWAY CLOSED!!

Ever wanted to ADOPT A SLOTH?
I've partnered with @beannbeancoffee for a truly special giveaway... the chance to symbolically adopt a sloth! Specifically, Lil' Sebastian here! You'll receive an adoption certificate featuring this cutie, plus more Bean & Bean goodies including a bag of Costa Rica coffee beans, steeped coffee bags, a Miir tumbler, sloth pin, tote bag, and signed copy of my book, "Be Everything At Once"!
 
How to enter:
1. Follow @dami_lee, @beannbeancoffee, and @theslothinstitute
2. Tag 3 friends you wanna have a cuppa with! 1 entry per person. 
This giveaway is open internationally, entries will be accepted until April 4th. You must be following all three to win! Bean&Bean will notify the winners by DM. Good luck!

Going live on the @ntwrk app today to talk about this print when it drops at 4pm EST! Thank you @estherlovesyou for inviting me to be a part of this women’s history month collection alongside amazing artists like @therealfafi @artbabygirl @nailsbymei @valfre @soyounlee 🥰 
It’s an 18”x24” print with a blind embossed signature, only available until 3/29 baybeee

node.text: Made this print for a special women’s history month collection for @ntwrk, curated by @estherlovesyou, an artist I’ve admired for a long time and look up to! 💕I’ll be going live with her tomorrow 3/19 at 4pm EST to talk about the print, which is a remake of one of my personal fave comics. It’ll be available exclusively on the @ntwrk app 3/22 4pm EST until 3/29. I know that’s a lot of dates and times so rest assured I will remind you again!!!
